---
// Pink gradient, left: rose gold iPhone + white circular accessory, right: "Upgrade Your Phone's Future", Shop Now, "Discover more" + arrow
---

<section class="bg-brand-pink py-16 md:py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-7xl flex-col items-center gap-12 px-4 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between md:gap-12 lg:px-8">
    <div class="flex-1 flex justify-center">
      <div class="relative h-80 w-64">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-[2rem] border-[10px] border-amber-200/90 bg-amber-50 shadow-xl" style="transform: rotate(-4deg);">
          <div class="absolute inset-2 rounded-[1.6rem] bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-500 to-pink-400" />
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -right-2 bottom-12 h-20 w-20 rounded-full border-4 border-white bg-white shadow-lg" />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex-1">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold leading-tight text-copy-dark sm:text-4xl">Upgrade Your Phone's Future</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-lg text-base text-copy-medium leading-relaxed">
        Get the most out of your device with our premium repair and accessory options. Quality you can trust.
      </p>
      <a href="#products" class="mt-6 inline-block rounded-lg bg-accent-pink px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-medium text-white hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">
        Shop Now
      </a>
      <p class="mt-4">
        <a href="#products" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm font-medium text-copy-dark hover:underline">
          Discover more
          <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
